citeinfo.title: Major roads of Indonesia (VMAP level 0, Ed. 5)

descript.abstract: This data displays the primary roads of Indonesia. It is a subset, for Indonesia, of the world wide product (VMAP level0 database Ed.5), produced by NGA (NIMA). The World Resources Institute prepared this dataset for use in the Interactive Atlas of Indonesia's Forests (2009).
